high_descs: Turn right, head to the curtains and hang a left to face the striped chair.
Pick up the gray remote on the left side of the striped chair.
Turn left, cross the room and hang a left just past the first couch cushion to face the small wooden table.
Place the remote on top of the wooden table just in front of the watch on the right side.
Head right, hang a left before the end of the couch, cross the room to the large wooden desk, turn left and then face the television to the right.
Pick up the gray remote in between the two black objects in front of the television.
Turn around, walk to the couch, head right and hang a right at the end of the first couch cushion to face the small wooden table.
Place the remote to the front and to the right of the plant on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Place two remote controls on a wooden table.
